Showing colSums()
[1] 60 64 68 72
In C++ element 0 is 60
In C++ element 1 is 64
In C++ element 2 is 68
In C++ element 3 is 72

I'll let you know if I get to the bottom of the runtime "can't find
libblas.so" error I got before.


